{
  "id": "6a28cab632cc04e14ba6bb62",
  "title": "無向辺と有向辺を同じように表したい",
  "created": 1781058231,
  "updated": 1781088011,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a28cab632cc04e14ba6bb62",
      "text": "無向辺と有向辺を同じように表したい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b1a",
      "text": "from [2026/06/10]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b1b",
      "text": " 無向辺と有向辺を同じように表したい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b1c",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b1d",
      "text": "\t数学の変数に代入する時にオーバーロードする方法を思いついた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b1e",
      "text": "\t\t[$ x=1\\ {\\rm and}\\ 2]とすると、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b1f",
      "text": "\t\t[$ x=1]が真かつ[$ x=2]が真になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b20",
      "text": "\t\t[$ x=3]とかは偽になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b21",
      "text": " \t何がしたいのか：グラフ理論の無向グラフを有向グラフと同じ型で表したい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293de00000000000630bd5",
      "text": " \t\t有向グラフ[$ G=(V,E)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087712,
      "updated": 1781087794
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b23",
      "text": " \t\t\t[$ a,b\\in V,\\ e=(a,b)\\in E\\sube V\\times V]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b24",
      "text": " \t\t無向グラフ[$ G=V,E]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b25",
      "text": " \t\t\t[$ a,b\\in V,\\ e=(a,b)\\ {\\rm and}\\ (b,a)\\in E\\sube V\\times V]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b26",
      "text": " \t\tよく見る無向グラフの定義は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b27",
      "text": " \t\t無向グラフ[$ G=V,E]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b28",
      "text": " \t\t\t[$ a,b\\in V,\\ e=\\{a,b\\}\\in E\\sube 2^V]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b29",
      "text": "   部分集合を使うのはインターフェイスの大きさが冗長",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b2a",
      "text": "   \t[$ |2^V|]もある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b2b",
      "text": "   \t実質的には[$ |V\\times V|]でいいのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b2c",
      "text": "   あ。部分集合はハイパーグラフで使える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b2d",
      "text": "   \t[$ e=\\{a,b\\}]と[$ e=\\{a,b,c\\}]と[$ e=\\{a,b,c,d\\}]を持つグラフとか作れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b2e",
      "text": "   ほな[$ E\\sube2^V]か～[ミルクボーイ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b2f",
      "text": "  当初の適用対象のつもりのものが無くなった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781058231
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cab70000000000d77b30",
      "text": "\t\tあーっと、更に前提が違うわ。グラフを定義する時は辺に直接代入せずに関数を噛ませるんだ。その方が色々柔軟になる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058231,
      "updated": 1781087805
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293e410000000000630bd7",
      "text": " \t\t[$ G=(V,E,\\mu)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087809,
      "updated": 1781087823
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293e530000000000630bd8",
      "text": " \t\t\t有向グラフ：[$ \\mu:E\\to V\\times V]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087827,
      "updated": 1781087853
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293e6e0000000000630bd9",
      "text": " \t\t\t無向グラフ：[$ \\mu:E\\to2^V]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087854,
      "updated": 1781087869
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293e920000000000630bda",
      "text": " \t\tこれだとタプルと集合の取り扱いの話になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087891,
      "updated": 1781087917
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293eac0000000000630bdb",
      "text": " \t\t\t[$ (a,b)]と[$ \\{a,b\\}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087917,
      "updated": 1781087925
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293eb70000000000630bdc",
      "text": " \t\t\t[$ a\\in\\{a,b\\}]に相当する[$ a\\in(a,b)]を表せるように[$ \\in]を定義しておけば大体同じように取り扱えるはず",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087927,
      "updated": 1781088011
    },
    {
      "id": "6a293e370000000000630bd6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781087799,
      "updated": 1781087799
    }
  ]
}